<p><a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/news-events/news/2018/07/plaque-unveiling-a-step-towards-truth-and-reconcilliation/">Plaque unveiling a step towards truth and reconciliation</a></p> 
<p><u><a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/news-events/news/2018/01/building-a-foundation-for-reconciliation/">Building a foundation for reconciliation</a></u></p>
    





